{"word":"Myrrh","slug":"myrrh","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Myrrh</b> A fragrant gum.<br/> A product of the land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=4&verse=6'>Son 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=4&verse=14'>Son 4:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=5&verse=1'>Son 5:1</a><br/> One of the compounds in the sacred anointing oil<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=23'>Exo 30:23</a><br/> Used as a perfume<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=12'>Est 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=45&verse=8'>Psa 45:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=7&verse=17'>Pro 7:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=3&verse=6'>Son 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=5&verse=13'>Son 5:13</a><br/> Brought by wise men as a present to Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=11'>Mat 2:11</a><br/> Offered to Jesus on the cross<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=23'>Mar 15:23</a><br/> Used for embalming<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=39'>Joh 19:39</a><br/> Traffic in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=25'>Gen 37:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=11'>Gen 43:11</a>"}]}